OL,3,C'It would be amazing' - Gareth Bale
OL,4,Cconfirms Cardiff City takeover plan
OL,6,FGareth Bale has confirmed that he is
OL,7,Fpart of a consortium looking to buy a
OL,8,Fcontrolling interest in his boyhood
OL,9,Fclub Cardiff City.
OL,11,FBale, who is Wales' all-time leading
OL,12,Fgoalscorer in the men's game,
OL,13,Fdescribed the prospect of linking up
OL,14,Fwith his hometown club as "a dream
OL,15,Fcome true".
OL,17,FThe group involving Bale reportedly
OL,18,Fmade an initial enquiry earlier this
OL,19,Fmonth, which was rejected by Bluebirds
OL,20,Fowner Vincent Tan.
