OL,3,C'It would be amazing' - Gareth Bale
OL,4,Cconfirms Cardiff City takeover plan
OL,6,FSpeaking on the red carpet at the
OL,7,Fpremiere for F1: The Movie, Bale told
OL,8,FSky Sports: "We are interested in
OL,9,Fgetting Cardiff. It's my home (town)
OL,10,Fclub, it's where I grew up and my
OL,11,Funcle used to play for them.
OL,13,F"To be involved with an ownership
OL,14,Fgroup would be a dream come true."
