OL,3,C'It would be amazing' - Gareth Bale
OL,4,Cconfirms Cardiff City takeover plan
OL,6,FBale had been linked with Cardiff
OL,7,Fafter leaving Real Madrid in 2022 but
OL,8,Fdecided to end his career with Los
OL,9,FAngeles FC.He was recently linked with
OL,10,Fa group that failed in a reported bid
OL,11,Fto take over Plymouth, who like
OL,12,FCardiff were relegated from the
OL,13,FChampionship last season.
OL,15,FThe Bluebirds are now playing in the
OL,16,Fthird tier of English football for the
OL,17,Ffirst time in over 20 years.
