OL,3,C'It would be amazing' - Gareth Bale
OL,4,Cconfirms Cardiff City takeover plan
OL,6,FBale added: "It is a club close to my
OL,7,Fheart. It's where I grew up and I
OL,8,Fwould love to be able to be a part of
OL,9,Fgrowing Cardiff and taking it to the
OL,10,FPremier League where it belongs.
OL,12,F"I know how amazing the Welsh fans and
OL,13,FCardiff fans are. It would be amazing
OL,14,Fto try and do something together.
OL,16,F"We are trying to engage with Cardiff
OL,17,Fand more news will come out on that in
OL,18,Fthe future but hopefully we can get
OL,19,Fsomething done."
